posting_body: ['508 Gulf Ave.', 'Wilmington, CA 90744', 'show contact info', 'Bay Pointe is located near the newly renovated Wilmington Waterfront Park.', 'So come and enjoy landscaping, playgrounds, performance grounds, and walking, bicycling and community events while living in the intimate community of Bay Pointe.', 'Bay Point offer 1 bedroom/ 1 bath unit reasonable space living room and dining room area, excellent storage space, stove and newly upgrade hardwood laminate floors.', 'Lease Terms', 'Lease: 12 Months', 'Rent: $1,400', 'Deposit: $1000*** O.A.C.', 'Unit Type: 1X1', 'Amenities:', '-Gas stove/oven', '-Controlled Access', '-Manager onsite', '-Laundry room onsite', '-Close to freeway 91, 105, and 110', 'Utilities:', '-Water and trash included', '-Resident pays electricity &gas', 'Income Requirement:', '-Application Fee: $ 50 per applicant', '-2 Month Paystubs or 2021 tax return', '-Government Issues Id', '-Social Security', '-Must make 2.5 x the rent (total net income)', 'CALL and Schedule you appointment today:', 'Maria', 'show contact info']
